  • Class Summary
    Class
    Description
    Citizen
    Main class from which all agents in the simulation inherit.
    Courier
    This implementation of the Citizen superclass represents an agent tasked with delivering the product between the location where it is produced, Plantation, and MobHeadquarters, where it is distributed to Dealer class agents.
    Dealer
    This implementation of the Citizen superclass represents an agent tasked with selling the product to RegularCitizen or TownVisitor.
    Item
    A class representing the item of a Citizen.
    Kingpin
    So, it turns out, this class is completely pointless.
    Police
    This implementation of the Citizen superclass represents an agent tasked with catching the Dealer and punishing RegularCitizen or TownVisitor for drug possession.
    Producer
    This implementation of the Citizen superclass represents an agent tasked with producing weed.
    RegularCitizen
    This implementation of the Citizen superclass represents an agent tasked with random movement.
    TownVisitor
    This implementation of the Citizen superclass represents an agent tasked with random appearing on the Map and random movement.
